928
00:58:24,946 --> 00:58:26,921
<b>Fazê-los sofrer.</font></b>

929
00:58:26,922 --> 00:58:29,359
<b>Olhar um tigre nos olhos.</font></b>

930
00:58:30,500 --> 00:58:34,076
